{
  "stem": "3964.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were liberating us, which it really was difficult to understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was impossible to comprehend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They brought us on land.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from land, by that time they had a mass of trucks, British trucks, had come to that site.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were several Red Cross trucks there that picked us up, gave us some food to eat, and took us to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was, of course, our-- our liberation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think anyone realized [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Took us to this hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll never forget this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were beds.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And here am I, [INAUDIBLE], who had survived with-- with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were looking at each other and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] are we dreaming or is-- is this real?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously, it was real.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unfortunately, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some of our friends, my friends, were liberated with me, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did not make it past that hospital, died in the hospital, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just weren't strong enough.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were strong enough to live, to survive, but not strong enough to live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's a terrible thing to see friends who you had gone through this terrible experience with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, the feeling of loss of friends after liberation to me was worse than the loss of friends during the Holocaust, during the concentration camp days, because you made it so long, you suffered so much [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to be free, to be a human being again, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then you cannot enjoy [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] your struggles, what you struggled for, what you fought for.",
      "word_count": 73
    }
  ],
